566
01:00:41,945 --> 01:00:44,016
- That's suicide.
- What's a quarantine?

567
01:00:44,181 --> 01:00:47,788
- It means they're not letting us out.
- The Breathers.

568
01:01:20,817 --> 01:01:22,728
Let us go!

569
01:01:22,886 --> 01:01:26,265
Let us go! Let us go!

570
01:01:26,423 --> 01:01:29,165
- Test them.
- Let us go! Let us out!

571
01:01:52,916 --> 01:01:55,863
Mom, it's an earthquake.

572
01:01:56,586 --> 01:01:59,294
No, sweetie, it can't be.

573
01:02:00,057 --> 01:02:02,628
Kingsville doesn't have earthquakes.

574
01:02:13,770 --> 01:02:16,478
Why the hell does the CDC
need military jets?

575
