581
01:02:56,146 --> 01:02:59,150
- I don't know if it's safe.
- Well, it's safer than here.

582
01:02:59,316 --> 01:03:00,761
Come on!

583
01:03:11,294 --> 01:03:13,171
- We gotta go, guys.
- Come on. Come on.

584
01:03:26,143 --> 01:03:27,293
- Where is it?
- There!

585
01:03:27,377 --> 01:03:29,288
- Where's the door?
- There.

586
01:03:37,888 --> 01:03:41,529
- They're coming! Hurry!
- Ray! Hurry!

587
01:03:44,794 --> 01:03:46,398
Let's go. Come on. I got you now.

588
01:03:47,464 --> 01:03:48,670
Claire, come on. Come on!

589
01:03:52,502 --> 01:03:53,947
Claire!

590
01:04:08,418 --> 01:04:11,797
Are you okay? Claire, are you okay?

591
01:04:13,156 --> 01:04:15,136
Yeah, I'm okay.

592
01:04:16,493 --> 01:04:17,767
- You guys?
- Yeah.

593
01:04:17,928 --> 01:04:21,535
